OL,3,CBody of woman found in River Ouse
OL,4,Cidentified
OL,6,FA woman whose body was pulled from the
OL,7,FRiver Ouse on Thursday 26 March has
OL,8,Fbeen identified.
OL,10,FPolice say the body has been formally
OL,11,Fidentified as that of a 56-year-old
OL,12,Fwoman from Hull but that they are not
OL,13,Fin a position to name her.
OL,15,FHer body was recovered from the water
OL,16,Fnear Cawood at around 12pm on Thursday
OL,17,Fby police working on a separate
OL,18,Finvestigation in the area.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
