OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774951543
OL,3,CBody of woman found in River Ouse
OL,4,Cidentified
OL,6,FOfficers say the death is being
OL,7,Ftreated as unexplained and that no
OL,8,Fsuspicious circumstances have been
OL,9,Funcovered so far.
OL,11,FA North Yorkshire Police spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid: "A report into the death is
OL,13,Fbeing compiled on behalf of the
OL,14,Fcoroner with support from Humberside
OL,15,FPolice.
OL,17,F"The woman's family have been informed
OL,18,Fand are receiving support from the
OL,19,Fpolice at this difficult time.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
