OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774951543
OL,3,CBody of woman found in River Ouse
OL,4,Cidentified
OL,6,F"Extensive enquiries are ongoing to
OL,7,Festablish the circumstances that led
OL,8,Fto her being in the water including
OL,9,Fwhere and when she entered the river."
